Package org.moeaframework.util.io

Collection of I/O utility classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommentedLineReader
    Read text from a character-input stream, ignoring lines starting with the # character.
    FileProtection
    Detects corrupted files using the MD5 message digest in a format compatible with the Unix command line utility md5sum.
    FileUtils
    Helper methods for working with files beyond what is provided by File.
    RedirectStream
    Redirects all content received by an InputStream to an OutputStream.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ValidationException
    Exception indicating a file could not be validated.
